      "protected_in_1988_arrete": "Listed in Arrêté 8 déc. 1988. IMPORTANT: for game/migratory species (brochet, truites, saumon, ombre, corégone, omble chevalier, aloses, lamproies marine/fluviatile) this protects EGGS/SPAWNING HABITAT — angling stays legal under size/season. TRUE no-take = only the non-game listed species: apron, bouvière, vandoise(s), ide, barbeau méridional, loche épineuse, loche d'étang, blennie fluviatile, lamproie de Planer. Esturgeon is no-take under Arrêté 20 déc. 2004 (NOT the 1988 one).",
      "invasive_R432_5": "Only perche-soleil and poisson-chat nationally. NOT silure, gobies, pseudorasbora, gambusie.",
      "cd_nom": "Read from live inpn.mnhn.fr/espece/cd_nom pages. null = not verified (do not guess)."
    },
